1. This dog is taller than that one. 2. The Ukraine is bigger than Belorussia.
3. That computer is more expensive than this one. 4. He is the tallest. 5. She is the
most beautiful girl. 6. The weather is worse today than yesterday. 7. Which of these
books is the most interesting? 8. March is not so cold as February. 9. My mother is
the most beautiful. 10. London is the best place for rest. 11. Sasha is younger than
Tom. 12. This building is the highest in our city. 13. He has fewer friends than I
have. 14. Anna has less work today than Sandra has. 15. These apples are sweeter
than those you brought yesterday.
